==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Thorough
<hw>Thor"ough</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Passing through;
<as>as, <ex>thorough</ex> lights in a house</as>.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Passing through or to the end; hence, complete;
perfect; <as>as, a <ex>thorough</ex> reformation; <ex>thorough</ex>
work; a <ex>thorough</ex> translator; a <ex>thorough</ex>
poet</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Thorough</ent>⟦br⟧

